SubjectSurtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods Remission Order
PrecisSURTAX ON THE IMPORTATION OF CERTAIN STEEL GOODS REMISSION ORDER in order to remit safeguard surtaxes already paid on imports of the goods excluded under the Order Amending the Surtax Order, covering the period between when safeguard measures were initially imposed (October 2018) and the day on which these Orders come into force.
